(13, '<p>Hi,</p><p>I was researching a bit on this and I found the description could be a broad statement that could be modified later. But then it seems not a good idea to be vague :). </p><p>I worked in the US as an IT consultant for a while, 15 years ago. I think it should be IT services.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>Regards,</p><p>SG</p>', 6, 166, NULL, '2025-05-07 16:34:15', '2025-05-07 16:34:15', NULL),
(14, '<p data-start=\"70\" data-end=\"102\" class=\"\">Thank you for the clarification!</p><p data-start=\"104\" data-end=\"267\" class=\"\">That makes perfect sense, and we appreciate you taking the time to look into it. We’ll proceed with <strong data-start=\"204\" data-end=\"221\">\"IT Services\"</strong> as the business description for your company.</p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p data-start=\"269\" data-end=\"348\" class=\"\">If you have any other preferences or updates, feel free to let us know anytime.</p>', 6, 76, NULL, '2025-05-08 06:10:37', '2025-05-08 06:10:37', NULL),
(15, '<p>Hello sir,</p><p>Thank you for your message.</p><p>We are pleased to inform you that we have successfully submitted your company formation application. The process typically takes 2–3 business days to complete.</p><p>We will notify you as soon as we receive any updates. Should you have any questions in the meantime, feel free to reach out.</p>', 6, 99, NULL, '2025-05-08 15:32:47', '2025-05-08 15:32:47', NULL),
(16, '<p>Thank you very much.&nbsp;</p><p>Regards,</p><p>SG</p>', 6, 166, NULL, '2025-05-08 20:10:45', '2025-05-08 20:10:45', NULL),
(17, '<p>Hi,</p><p>I received the formation documents. Thank you. Please let me know further processing steps.</p><p>Regards,</p><p>SG</p>', 6, 166, NULL, '2025-05-15 17:20:50', '2025-05-15 17:20:50', NULL),
(18, '<p>Hello&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Urvish,&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"><br></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Your Company formation process is completed. The documents are provided on your dashboard.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Additionally,&nbsp;</span>beginning January 1, 2024, the Biden administration requires owners and certain representatives of each newly formed small business entity to upload a photo ID and register with the Financial Crimes Enforcement Network (FinCEN). Failure to register within 90 days may result in criminal prosecution, including up to two years of imprisonment and a $10,000 fine. </p><p>Find out more about this law at <a href=\"http://www.fincen.gov/boi.\" target=\"_blank\">www.fincen.gov/boi.</a></p><p><br></p><p>Thank you.</p>', 8, 104, NULL, '2025-05-27 06:41:59', '2025-05-27 06:41:59', NULL),
